        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[DeletedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[IsAdultOnly], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [t] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [t].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [o].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [t0].[Id]

SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [o].[ProductId], [t].[Name] AS [ProductName], COALESCE(SUM([o].[Quantity]), 0) AS [TotalSold], COALESCE(SUM(CAST([o].[Quantity] AS decimal(18,2)) * [o].[UnitPrice]), 0.0) AS [Revenue]
FROM [OrderItems] AS [o]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)

GROUP BY [o].[ProductId], [t].[Name]

) AS `t` ON `p`.`CategoryId` = `t`.`Id`
